        "text": "## Pb²⁺–Chloride Stability Constant with ≥2 Literature Citations\n\n### The Measurement\n\nEvery one of the 20 VLM entries (vlm_1 through vlm_20) for the Pb²⁺–Cl⁻ system carries **exactly 2 linked literature citations**. Here is a representative example using **vlm_1**:\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| VLM ID | vlm_1 |\n| System | Pb²⁺ + Cl⁻ → PbCl⁺ (ML complex) |\n| Constant type | log β (overall) |\n| log β value | **1.59** |\n| Temperature | 25 °C |\n| Ionic strength | 0 mol/L (infinite dilution) |\n| Solvent | Water |\n| Citation count | **2** |",
